   "source": [
    "#Conversion to datetime format\n",
    "df[\"Created Date\"]=pd.to_datetime(df[\"Created Date\"])\n",
    "df[\"Closed Date\"]=pd.to_datetime(df[\"Closed Date\"])"

  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 12,
   "id": "dccdb2e8",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "#Creating a new column ‘Request_Closing_Time’ as the time elapsed between request creation and request closing\n",
    "df[\"Request_Closing_Time\"]=(df[\"Closed Date\"]-df[\"Created Date\"])\n",
    "Request_Closing_Time=[]\n",
    "for x in (df[\"Closed Date\"]-df[\"Created Date\"]):\n",
    "    close=x.total_seconds()/60\n",
    "    Request_Closing_Time.append(close)\n",
    "df[\"Request_Closing_Time\"]=Request_Closing_Time"
   ]
  },

   "source": [
    "data_crosstab = pd.crosstab( chi_sq[\"Location Type\"],chi_sq[\"Complaint Type\"])"

   "source": [
    "stat, p, dof, expected = chi2_contingency(data_crosstab) \n",
    "\n",
    "alpha = 0.05\n",
    "if p <= alpha: \n",
    "    print('Dependent (reject H0)') \n",
    "else: \n",
    "    print('Independent (H0 holds true)')"
   ]
